      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this meticulously maintained masterpiece. Presented in true showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, boasting a flawless exterior and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every detail has been preserved with exacting standards, ensuring a driving experience that is as smooth as it is sophisticated. For the collector or the enthusiast who demands nothing less than the extraordinary, this is an unrivaled opportunity to own a vehicle of rare pedigree and uncompromising quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
